{"id":4386,"title":"[Investigation on schistosomiasis japonica infection and preventive knowledge of immigration population in Jinshan District, Shanghai].","abstract":"To investigate the schistosomiasis japonica infection and preventive knowledge of immigration population in Jinshan District, Shanghai so as to provide the evidence for improving the control work.The immigration population from schistosomiasis endemic provinces and local people were screened by serum IHA screening for schistosome infection, and the positives were further examined by Kato-Katz technique and the miracidium hatching method. The schistosomiasis preventive knowledge and behaviors were investigated by questionnaires.A total of 579 were investigated with 348 immigration people and 231 local people, and among them, the male accounted for 72.0% and female accounted for 28.0%. In the immigration population, the main age group was 20-29 (56.0%), and 56.6% of the immigration had an education level at senior middle school or higher. The most proportion of immigration was from Anhui Province (36.2%). There were 4 IHA positive persons (1.15%) in the immigration, and 1 was positive in the stool test, and the schistosome infection rate was 0.29%. There were no positives in the local people. The schistosomiasis preventive knowledge of the immigration was generally poor, and some people' s behaviors of see doctor and medication were incorrect.There are schistosome infected persons among the immigration population from schistosomiasis endemic provinces, and their schistosomiasis prevention knowledge was poor, thus there is a schistosomiasis transmission risk.","date":"2014-10-27","categories":"Parasitic Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25345167","annotations":[{"name":"Infection","weight":0.772178,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Infection"},{"name":"Pharmaceutical drug","weight":0.650591,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pharmaceutical_drug"},{"name":"Male","weight":0.471548,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Male"},{"name":"Shanghai","weight":0.444348,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shanghai"},{"name":"Anhui","weight":0.435303,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anhui"},{"name":"Feces","weight":0.418716,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Feces"},{"name":"Endemism","weight":0.355845,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Endemism"},{"name":"Schistosoma japonicum","weight":0.311156,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Schistosoma_japonicum"},{"name":"Education","weight":0.2769,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Education"},{"name":"Preventive medicine","weight":0.263883,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Preventive_medicine"},{"name":"Immigration","weight":0.245686,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Immigration"},{"name":"Schistosomiasis","weight":0.235256,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Schistosomiasis"},{"name":"Middle school","weight":0.20333,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Middle_school"},{"name":"Population","weight":0.18053,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Population"},{"name":"Female","weight":0.142407,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Female"},{"name":"Physician","weight":0.101782,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Physician"},{"name":"School","weight":0.0805305,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/School"},{"name":"Knowledge","weight":0.045004,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Knowledge"},{"name":"Risk","weight":0.0391252,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Risk"},{"name":"Blood plasma","weight":0.0300804,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Blood_plasma"},{"name":"Screening (medicine)","weight":0.0300804,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Screening_(medicine)"},{"name":"Evidence","weight":0.0300804,"wikiped